These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, writing, collecting, photography
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, disaster, drama, action
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is the person watching action movies##1
3. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Hobby          | photography | collecting | writing | baking   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster  | sports     | drama   | action |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, august, october, may
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, helicopter, boat, airplane
1. the person who's birthday is in may is the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
5. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Birthday   | october | may | august | june    |
| Transport   | boat    | helicopter      | car | airplane |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
City: paris, miami, colone, hamburg
4 different games are played: scrabble, go, monopoly, domino
1. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing domino##1
2. the person traveling to paris is the person playing scrabble##1
3. the person playing go is on the far right##1
4. the person playing domino is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
5. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| City         | paris | hamburg | colone   | miami |
| Game   | scrabble   | monopoly | domino | go         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
4 different games are played: domino, bridge, canasta, billiard
House: art-deco, palace, craftsman, tower
1. the palace house is the person playing billiard##1
2. the person playing bridge is on the left of the craftsman house##1
3. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing domino##1
4. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
5. the art-deco house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Game   | billiard | bridge | domino  | canasta      |
| House         | palace | tower   | craftsman | art-deco |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
House: art-deco, craftsman, cottage, gothic-revival
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, july, june, december
1. the craftsman house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the cottage house##1
3. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| House   | gothic-revival | cottage | craftsman | art-deco |
| Birthday    | january       | december | june | july     |

