.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, may, september, november
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, quad-bike, car, ship
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
5. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Birthday   | november | september | october | may |
| Transport           | jet-ski      | car | ship | quad-bike    |

