.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, canasta, bridge, poker
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, horror, epic, documentary
1. the person watching epic movies is on the far left##1
2. the person playing poker is on the far right##1
3. the person playing bridge is on the far left##1
4. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
5. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Game   | bridge | canasta | scrabble | poker  |
| Movie-Genre           | epic | sports | documentary       | horror |

