.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, american, russian, indian
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, ambient, house, soul
1. the fan of soul is on the right of the american##1
2. the fan of soul is the indian##1
3. the american is on the right of the chinese##1
4. the russian is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
5. the fan of d&b is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Nationality         | russian | chinese      | american | indian |
| Music-Genre   | d&b          | ambient | house     | soul    |

