2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Birthday   | may    | october       | april | august   |
| Hobby     | reading | writing | dancing   | baking |

