.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, puzzles, skydiving, camping
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, december, august, july
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far left##1
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Hobby      | skydiving | puzzles  | writing | camping |
| Birthday   | november  | august | july           | december   |

