.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-12::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, teacher, entrepreneur, coach
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, montecristo, alhambra, pall-mall
1. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the electrician##1
2. the entrepreneur is on the right of the coach##1
3. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the game-smoker##1
4. the electrician is on the right of the teacher##1
5. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the electrician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Job   | teacher | electrician | coach | entrepreneur  |
| Cigar           | pall-mall | montecristo      | alhambra | game |

