.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-13::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, daisy, azalea, marigold
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, baking, rock-climbing, magic-tricks
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person who growslily##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who growslily##1
3. the person who growsazalea is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
5. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Flower   | azalea | daisy  | lily | marigold   |
| Hobby        | rock-climbing | baking | magic-tricks    | gardening |

