.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, traveling, singing, puzzles
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, green, mauve, white
1. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who likes green##1
2. the person who likes white is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
4. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
5. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |    4     |
| Hobby   | singing | puzzles     | rock-climbing | traveling |
| Color         | white | green | blood-red   | mauve   |

