2. the person traveling to prague is on the far left##1
3. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
4. the person playing poker is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
5. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4        |
| City           | prague | london    | berlin    | boston |
| Game   | billiard      | snooker | poker | bridge       |

