.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-17::.
4 different pets are kept: hamster, cat, fish, goat
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, 7up, lemonade, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the owner of the fish##1
2. the owner of the hamster is the person drinking 7up##1
3. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |    3    |   4    |
| Pet   | cat      | fish | goat | hamster |
| Beverage     | coffee | hot-chocolate    | lemonade  | 7up |

