.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-18::.
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, artichoke, eggplant, cucumber
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, pink, azure, amber
1. the person eating pumpkin is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes chestnut is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
4. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
5. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person who likes amber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Food      | pumpkin   | cucumber | artichoke   | eggplant      |
| Color   | chestnut | amber      | pink | azure |

