.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-19::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, techno, gospel, house
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, milk, 7up, tea
1. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of house##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
3. the person drinking 7up is the fan of gospel##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the left of the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre         | techno | gospel | house | funk |
| Beverage   | tea     | 7up    | cola      | milk   |

