.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
4 different pets are kept: mouse, ferret, guinea-pig, dog
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, soy-milk, juice, water
1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the owner of the dog is the person drinking water##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Pet   | mouse | guinea-pig | ferret | dog   |
| Beverage     | juice  | cola    | soy-milk       | water |

 